Subject: [PATCH] Add workflow to remind updating CLAUDE.md on structure changes

This patch adds a GitHub Actions workflow that creates an issue reminder
when project structure changes are detected, prompting maintainers to
review and update the CLAUDE.md documentation accordingly.

